 – 1279  AD ), was put to death by the then emperor."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Galtha e Praers was born in 1120, in England. She married Richard de Praers II about 1132, in Blacon, Chester, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 5 sons. She died in 1144, in England, United Kingdom, at the age of 24."},"et":{"1120–1144":"1120–1144","1117–1167":"1117–1167","1138–Male":"1138–Surnud","1140–1190":"1140–1190","1140–1219":"1140–1219","1166–1233":"1166–1233","1190":"1190","1117":"1117","1138":"1138","1233":"1233","1167":"1167","1144":"1144","1166":"1166","1120":"1120","1140":"1140","about 1132":"umbes 1132","1219":"1219","Dutton, Cheshire, England":"Dutton, Cheshire, England","Chester, Cheshire, England":"Blacon, Chester, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Nantwich, Cheshire, England":"Nantwich, Cheshire, England","Sudbury, Suffolk, England":"Sudbury, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1120–1144":"1120–1144","1117–1167":"1117–1167","1138–Male":"1138–Kuollut","1140–1190":"1140–1190","1140–1219":"1140–1219","1166–1233":"1166–1233","1190":"1190","1117":"1117","1138":"1138","1233":"1233","1167":"1167","1144":"1144","1166":"1166","1120":"1120","1140":"1140","about 1132":"noin 1132","1219":"1219","Dutton, Cheshire, England":"Dutton, Cheshire, England","Chester, Cheshire, England":"Blacon, Chester, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Nantwich, Cheshire, England":"Nantwich, Cheshire, England","Sudbury, Suffolk, England":"Sudbury, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1120–1144":"1120–1144","1117–1167":"1117–1167","1138–Male":"1138–Décédé","1140–1190":"1140–1190","1140–1219":"1140–1219","1166–1233":"1166–1233","1190":"1190","1117":"1117","1138":"1138","1233":"1233","